M.B., Appellant/Petitioner(s),
v.
DEPT. OF CHILDREN & FAMILIES, Appellee/Respondent(s). CASE NO.: 2D18-4299 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Second District. January 17, 2019

BY ORDER OF THE COURT:

Because M.B. has failed to serve an initial brief as provided by this court's order of December 12, 2018, this appeal is dismissed for failure to prosecute.

CASANUEVA, MORRIS, ROTHSTEIN-YOUAKIM, JJ., Concur.
